Feature: REST API Extensions

    Scenario: Extension list with one extension
        Given I have the following extensions:
            | exten | context |
            | 1523  | default |
        When I access the list of extensions
        Then I get a list containing the following extensions:
            | exten | context |
            | 1523  | default |

